The problem (3) has been treated by Kassara 
[23] and Kassara and Moustafid 
[24] in the framework of the set-valued approach for a class of ODE immunotherapy models. Such models was expressed by a non-linear control system (1), in the particular case, where the dynamics f (1a) is affine in control u, and the Eq.(1b) is given as follows4\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
